data.description: Well-maintained 5b/3b home in Tuscany Community. The home features the 1st floor bedroom and a full bath. Dining room with tray ceiling, chair rail, wainscoting & crown. Huge mater bedroom. Community Pool, clubhouse and play areas. Very convenient to schools, shopping & major highways.
